snippet.title: MetaOps Game Trailer | First-Person Shooter | Multiplayer
snippet.description:
Join the battlefield and team up with your friends to put your tactical skills to the test within MetaOps, a first-person shooter built on Unity. Game Modes: Multiplayer, Campaign (soon) and Battle Royale (soon)

MetaOps harnesses the power of blockchain gaming, providing players with ownership of their earned assets to keep, trade or sell.

The game is currently in Alpha, playable and fully released later this year (2022).

MetaOps was created by a #blockchain company, Open Portal Studios, with the mission to place more power in the hands of the players by providing connection to the #metaverse via in-game NFTs. 

FOLLOW US: 
📂 Discord: https://discord.gg/metaops
🎥 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@metaopsgaming
